```
DOTFILES

Bash Config

1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/kuwarte/dotfiles.git

2. Create Backup (e.g.)
cp ~/.bashrc ~/.bashrc.backup

3. Copy the cloned specific file to replace current config (e.g.)
cp ~/dotfiles/wsl/.bashrc ~/.bashrc

Editor Config

Please refer to the documentation in init-nvim.sh for instructions on setting up and using the Neovim configuration included in this repository.
```
